works.description: Yeastie Boys, the brewing brainchild of local brewer Stu McKinlay and New Zealand’s most notorious beer hunter Sam Possenniskie, is all set to release the Rex Attitude, the world’s first whisky beer. The Rex Attitude is the world’s first single-malt, peat-smoked golden ale. The use of 100% heavily peated Scottish distilling malt results in one of the smokiest beers ever. The Yeastie Boys have already imported two tonnes of Scottish malt that’s needed specifically for the Rex Attitude.
